front.title: •Home One
front.gametext: May add unlimited pilots, passengers, vehicles and starfighters. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilots provide total ability of 4. Immune to attrition < 8 (< 10 when Ackbar piloting).
front.lore: Command ship of the Rebel fleet. 1200 meters long. Masterpiece of aesthetic form. Most heavily armed and armored ship in the fleet. Admiral Ackbar's personal flagship.

combo: Wokling (V) pulls Launching The Assault which pulls Home One
Home One + Admiral Ackbar + First Officer Thaneespi
